These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, lemonade, tea
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, helicopter, car, bus
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, gardening, puzzles, writing
4 different games are played: domino, mah-jongg, bridge, backgammon
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, mauve, brown, grey
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, climbing, rugby, skiing
 1. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is the person who likes black##1
 3. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
 4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 5. the person drinking tea is the person driving the bus##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 7. the person playing bridge is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who likes grey##2
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 9. the person who likes black is on the right of the person playing domino##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person playing bridge and the person driving the bus##2
11. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
12. the person playing backgammon is the person who's hobby is writing##1
13. the person who likes brown is between the person who likes mauve and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | tea        | coffee       | lemonade  | almond-milk |
| Transport          | bus     | car         | helicopter     | tram    |
| Hobby         | gardening  | fishing      | puzzles   | writing     |
| Game           | mah-jongg | domino | bridge   | backgammon     |
| Color   | mauve    | brown         | black | grey         |
| Sport         | skiing     | baseball     | climbing  | rugby       |

