The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, filmmaking, skydiving, writing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, thriller, time-travel, western
4 different games are played: bridge, chess, snooker, billiard
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, fuchsia, lavender, chestnut
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, climbing, water-polo, skateboarding
 1. the person who likes fuchsia is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
 2. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
 4. the person who likes fuchsia is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
 5. the person playing bridge is the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 8. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person watching action movies and the person who's hobby is writing##2
 9. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's hobby is writing##1
10. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left##1
11. the person playing bridge is the person watching time-travel movies##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
13. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
14. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | sprite    | fanta       | soy-milk   | almond-milk |
| Hobby         | chess     | skydiving   | writing    | filmmaking  |
